# ===================== Vite Environment =====================
# Vite exposes environment variables prefixed with `VITE_` to client code.
# Keep secrets out of frontend env for production. Use server-side secrets where
# appropriate.

# Firebase API key (used by client SDK). This is okay to expose for Firebase.
VITE_FIREBASE_APIKEY=AIzaSyBrDNVYx4T8IFw8L-bouw4yHaR5R5DChsM

# Optional: Backend server URL used by the frontend client. Set via Vite:
# VITE_SERVER_URL=https://localhost:8000
# (Uncomment and set when you want to override the default local server.)

